   version stable 5.63 5.62 5.61 5.50
   require perl--ExtUtils-ParseXS
    switch -t '' to build a thread-safe version of the module
    switch -x '' to exclude support for SHA-384/512
  category perl
 attribute perl-module
    source http://www.cpan.org/authors/id/M/MS/MSHELOR/Digest-SHA-$VERSION.tar.gz
      info last 20111113
      info home http://search.cpan.org/search?dist=Digest-SHA
      desc 'complete implementation of the NIST Secure Hash Standard
It gives Perl programmers a convenient way to calculate
SHA-1, SHA-224, SHA-256, SHA-384, and SHA-512 message digests.
The module can handle all types of input, including partial-byte data.'
